  <MissileTypes>
    <MissileTemplate>
      <AssociatedTemplateName>SGM-109 </AssociatedTemplateName>
      <Designation>SGM-109</Designation>
      <Nickname />
      <Description>$MISSILEGUIDANCE_MODE_DIRECT - $MISSILESEEKER_MODE_PASSIVE_ABBREV(&lt;color=#D4211D&gt;WAKE&lt;/color&gt;) - $MISSILEWARHEAD_SHORT_HEIMPACT</Description>
      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SGM-109 &lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 1 direct guidance missile.  It is based on the SGM-1 body, which is a nimble general-purpose missile.  This missile will deliver a $MISSILEWARHEAD_DETAIL_HEIMPACT warhead.  It homes in on its target using a Passive Wake seeker.

$MISSILESTAT_CONTROLMETHOD: $MISSILEGUIDANCE_MODE_DIRECT
